Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No!
